sequenceDiagram
  participant U as Usuario
  participant UI as Frontend
  participant API as Backend

  U->>UI: Navega a /properties/:id/apply/start
  UI->>API: GET /properties/:id
  API-->>UI: property
  UI->>U: Muestra resumen (start)
  U->>UI: Click "Ver si califico"
  UI->>API: POST /applications/prequalify
  API-->>UI: prequalification + documentChecklist
  UI->>U: Muestra resultado y checklist
  U->>UI: Sube documentos y envía
  UI->>API: POST /requests (payload)
  API-->>UI: request created
  UI->>U: Redirige a /apply/review
